@NODE QUICKHELP "Visual Arts Built-In Functions -- Quick Help"

The following are Visual Arts built-in functions.  Look in VisualArts.h
file of further prototypes.


SPEECH FUNCTIONS
----------------

NAME      InitSpeech -- Initializes the speech module

SYNOPSIS  status = InitSpeech(void)

